Pension Yojana Rajasthan Form in Hindi (PDF) \u2013 OfflineRajasthan Vidhwa Pension Yojana Eligibility CriteriaCandidates have to visit the official website rajssp.raj.nic.inAt the homepage, click at the \u201cEligibility Criteria\u201d section in the header or directly click this linkAll the women above the age of 18 years who are Widow / Divorced or Left Out by Husbands are eligible for Mukhyamantri Akel Narri Pension Scheme.To avail pension, the annual income of the family of the applicant must not exceed Rs. 48,000 per annumPension For Women \u2013Women between the age of 18 to 59 years will get a monthly pension of Rs. 500.Women between the age of 60 to 74 years will get a monthly pension of Rs. 1000.All the Women above the age of 75 years will get a monthly pension of Rs. 1500.All the pensioners can check their eligibility criteria through the Bhamashah Details \u2013 Check Pensioner Eligibility through Bhamashah Details"}